If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Approved
body: On June 25, 2021, we approved your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190142998. We sent you an approval notice. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your approval notice by July 10, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
